Sandy Harris writes:
> Erik Andersen wrote:
>> This is kernel space.  Using any math functions is forbidden
>> in kernel space,
>
> Exactly what do you mean by "forbidden"?
You will corrupt the FPU registers of a user app and/or
cause an oops, assuming the kernel compiles at all.
